{
  "stem": "365.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We went out to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When we came back from work, we were marched past them to show us, this is the punishment for things.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When they were taken out, they were half dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were 12 hours in the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] it went through my mind that I have to survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In order to tell the world of what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was unbelievable or incomprehensible that people could imagine something like that, that that is possible that-- of what one human being can do to another.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I pictured myself that if somebody would tell me a story like this, I would not want to believe them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So therefore, I made it almost a vow if I-- to survive and to be able.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was my way, almost, of fighting back, is to show them that I will survive, that I can make it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was my resistance, not to give in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was sent, eventually-- it was in May, late in May, where I was eventually chosen to be sent to a forced labor camp, a regular forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That camp was called Graditz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the vicinity of Breslau, not far from Breslau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This camp was located in a former flour mill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It must have been about 10,000 square feet of floor space for where we were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were crammed in close to 3,000 people in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were sleeping on shelves, three shelves, just like sardines in a can, squeezed in one next to the other.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If one turned, he pushed against the other one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The conditions of living as far as torture and beating wasn't as cruel and as hard as was Brande.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the hygiene conditions were much worse, to the extreme.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
